{"tid":1740034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足：今次Poly準備不足，帶咗好多麻煩，好對唔住！辛苦大家！","createTime":"2019-11-19T22:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T22:36:18.000Z","uid":295295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"11ebdb324fd62afda30c07148936843b12b45369","tid":1740034,"uid":295295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wZVCSsN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZVCSsN.jpg&h=d23f6e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3日前成功進入理大校園支援手足，3日後決定行出去，即使背負着犯有暴動罪的風險，阿魚卻不曾後悔3天前的決定，「我喺呢一刻仲未有流血已經好好，入得嚟Poly，點樣都有呢個心理準備嘅」。事後回想起當天到理大的路程上未有受到警方阻撓，不禁令阿魚懷疑，其實政府或警方早有計劃要將抗爭者引到學校內作出圍捕，當天來到理大支援時，並沒有考慮太多，只是不想有手足白白「送頭」。阿魚曾經有怪責過當初呼籲大家留守的理大學生，「本身有怪過Poly嘅手足嘅，但見到段嘢，點怪啫」，阿魚指向前方由理大學生用噴漆在玻璃門上噴上的道歉宣言，「各位手足：今次Poly準備不足，帶咗好多麻煩，好對唔住！辛苦大家！」，不禁失笑起來。"},{"pid":"a2635b6d9e7d5ac3ccbc3c84fdbe8288392e7a6d","tid":1740034,"uid":295295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191119/60284686?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60284686%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=3c03be2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60284686%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6566d82a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191119/60284686?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"b50d1aefd14ea99c09b092bf911c0cf6094de3df","tid":1740034,"uid":295295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:36:18.000Z","msg":"大家繼續努力，黎明行動見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}